  "notes": "Bashkir in Cyrillic script (Russia). Distinctive interdentals: Ҙ = /ð/, Ҫ = /θ/ — unusual among Turkic. Ҡ = /q/ (uvular stop); Ғ = /ʁ/; Ң = /ŋ/; Һ = /h/. 9-vowel system with harmony.",
